   (ART ADV: Photo has been sent to NYT photo clients.)
</P>
<P>
   CIR-ELDER-CARE (Undated) _ How the Web assists in care of
elderly. By Catherine Greenman.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; HOME (Moved in ``l'' category) &LR;  &QL;
