   AUTOMOTIVE NEWS
</P>
<P>
   COXNET WHEELS PAGE
</P>
<P>
   EDs: This is the CoxNet WHEELS page for the current week. This
layout is available now.
</P>
<P>
   COXNET WHEELS 0801 _ Although available in other parts of the
world for some time, it's only now that BMW's compact 323i sport
wagon, read station wagon, is available in the United States. It
can only enhance sales of the 3-Series line. (DeVault, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) Art includes a 3-column color photo of the
2000 323i sport wagon and a 2-column color photo of the car's
steering wheel.
</P>
