<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-03 12:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1600 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a BC-CPT-TECH-MICROSOFT-BO     08-03 1614
