   ISRAEL-EGYPT (Cairo) _ Israeli Prime Minister Ehud Barak, facing
a deadline to make peace with the Palestinians, met with Egypt's
president, Hosni Mubarak, to try to persuade him to help break the
impasse over Jerusalem's future. By Susan Sachs.
</P>
