<P>
   ENTERTAINMENT/ARTS
</P>
<P>
   EMINEM _ In the tradition of NWA, Marilyn Manson and others,
Eminem, who appears here tonight, sings to shock. Unlike the
others, his is enjoying phenomenal mainstream commercial success;
his song about having sex with his mother is on the radio. This at
a time when ever-younger kids are into mainstream music, lured by
the likes of Disney Channel videos and Disney Radio. What are
boomer parents, who fought their own parents to hear Jim Morrison's
Oedipal rant, to do? Censor and be old fogies or let kids hear
songs of rape and homophobia? (Harris, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 35.
</P>
