<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    HERE'S A COUPLE OF POLITICAL SECRETS
 &HT;    Moving in the (k) commentary and (p) political categories for
release Sunday, Aug. 6.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
