<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-03 17:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1921 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u p BC-VENNOCHI-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      08-03 0796
