and given 10 years unsupervised probation. Effectively, Brunswick
washed its hands of him, ordered him to get out of a five-county
judicial circuit and stay away for 10 years. Presto: No longer
Brunswick's problem. Change-o: Now others' problem. (Waco
Tribune-Herald) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
