   If you have questions or need a resend, please call CoxNet, the
Cox News Service, at 404-526-5456.
</P>
<P>
   EARTHLINK-FOLO _ ATLANTA _ Following developments based on
Charles Brewer's departure from EarthLink. (Staff, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) 15.
</P>
<P>
   SOUTHERNERS-BADRAP _ A study out of Texas says people with
Southern drawls get a bad rap on the job. The study had human
resources directors rank accents from around the country and then
assign jobs to the speakers they heard. Y'all guessed it:
Southerners were viewed as dumb, got low marks and were put in jobs
where they had little contact with the public or customers.
(Joyner, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) 10.
</P>
