<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   KASHMIR-MASSACRES (Chattisinghpora, India) _ The latest
massacres in Kashmir follow the same pattern as past attacks:
Everybody points the finger at everybody else. First face-to-face
talks between India and guerrillas in 11 years take place. By
Indira A.R. Lakshmanan. 1400 words.
</P>
<P>
