<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-03 19:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2020 &Cx1f; tad-z
u f BC-GAPOWER-BIAS0804-COX     08-03 0620
