<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
  The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Aug. 4 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Joe Jares at (818) 713-3602. 
 
 
BBN-LOPES (Los Angeles) _ Feature on Milwaukee Brewers manager
Davey Lopes. 
By Matt McHale. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBN-DODNOTE (Los Angeles) _ Los Angeles Dodgers notebook. 
By Brian Dohn. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
FBC-MODESTI-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ From Pac-10 media day: five of
the 10 coaches are on the hot seat. 
By Kevin Modesti. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBA-WISE (Anaheim, Calif.) _ Former Pepperdine pitcher Matt Wise
joined the Anaheim Angels. 
By Frank Girardot/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
FBC-PAC10 (Los Angeles) _ Short article on predicted order of
finish this season. 
