</P>
<P>
   ROCKPORT-AD-COLUMN (Undated) _ An offbeat new campaign embraces
the philosophy of the comedian Jeff Foxworthy in declaring: ``No
shirt. No shoes. No problem!'' And what in the world are the
shirtless hunks and hunkettes peddling in the ads? Shoes, made by
the Rockport Co. By Stuart Elliott. (Scheduled to move by 8:30 p.m.
ET.)
</P>
<P>
   BIZGLANCE (Undated) _ Digest of the day's financial stories.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET.)
</P>
</TEXT>
