   NATIONAL (``a'' category)
</P>
<P>
   SCHOOLS-TEXAS (Austin) _ Texas education leaders for years have
tinkered with the standards by which schools are rated, often
postponing tougher measures in election years, critics say, in
hopes of projecting a better image of what goes on in classrooms.
By KATHY WALT.
</P>
